  <brief_title>Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of CJ-30060 in Hypertensive Patients With Hyperlipidemia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-blind, Randomized, Multi-center Phase III Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of CJ-30060 Compared With Amlodipine/Valsartan Combination Therapy and Valsartan/Rosuvastatin Combination Therapy in Hypertensive Patients With Hyperlipidemia</official_title>
