  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the safety and efficacy of CJ-30060 compared with amlodipine/valsartan
      combination therapy and valsartan/rosuvastatin combination therapy in hypertensive patients
      with hyperlipidemia
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
